      <h1>Welcome to our Guides section!</h1>
      <p>Have an unanswered question about who we are and what we do? Experiencing an issue that you'd like resolved? Wondering how you can contribute? You're in the right place. The guides are structured in the following sections:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>General</li>
        <li>Shop / Ranks</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We hope these help. If you need assistance, please reach out to someone from our Staff Team. Staff are available to answer questions and wear their STAFF tag in-game. You can also shoot us an email at <a href="mailto:<%= contactemail %>"><%= contactemail %></a> or find us in our <a href="/discord">public Discord server</a>.</p>
      <p>If you spot any mistakes or gray areas in this guide, do please reach out as we'd want that fixed! Email <a href="mailto:<%= contactemail %>"><%= contactemail %></a> or talk to one of our Staff Members.</p>
      <p>Thanks,<br>Crafting For Christ Staff Team</p>
