            <h4 id="list-item-3">I didn't get my rank!</h4>
              <p>If you have waited 12 hours and haven't received your rank or other purchased items, it is likely there was an issue handling your payment. Be sure to contact our <a href="mailto:<%= contactemail %>">Support Team</a> if you are in this position and we'll be sure to sort it out as soon as possible.</p>
            <h4 id="list-item-4">Can I transfer my rank to a different account?</h4>
              <p>Ranks purchased are strictly not transferrable, You may not move your rank from one Minecraft account to another.</p>
            <h4 id="list-item-5">I didn't get my rank in Discord!</h4>
